<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <h4>{{t "Your Dashboard" key="app_dashboard"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <img src={{path "images/dashboard.png"}} alt="" style='width: 100%;' >
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12' style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "The dashboard is your home base — it's the first thing you see when you log in." key="dashboard_1"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "From here you can check notifications, manage your profile, adjust settings, and browse available boards." key="dashboard_2"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Communicator accounts can be set to skip the dashboard and go straight to their home board." key="communicators_skip_dashboard"}}</li>
  </ul>
</div>
